  volume    =  571,
  number    =  216345,
  pages     =  216345,
  abstract  = "Pancreatic cancer is one of the common malignant tumors of the
               digestive system and is known as the ``king of cancers''. It is
               extremely difficult to diagnose at an early stage, the disease
               progresses rapidly, and the effect of chemotherapy and
               radiotherapy is poor, so the prognosis of pancreatic cancer
